Package: specsimfts
Type: Package
Title: Temperature Conversion Package for Demonstration
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: c(person("Tomas", "Rubin", email = "tomas.rubin@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")), person("Victor", "Panaretos", email = "victor.panaretos@epfl.ch", role = c("aut")))
Description: The packages provides a toolbox of simulation method in the spectral
	domain using harmonic Karhunen-Loeve decomposition approach or filtered white
	noise approach, and allows for simulation of FARFIMA processes. The demo files
	contain code snippets allowing for easy modification and quick deployment.
Depends: R (>= 4.0.0)
Imports:
	pracma,
	mvtnorm,
	expm
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
RoxygenNote: 7.1.0
